msgid "Connector extension classes"
msgstr "连接器扩展类"

msgid ""
"Most applications should use module-level ``ray.klein.read_*`` functions "
"and :class:`~ray.klein.DataStream` writer methods. The classes below are "
"public extension contracts for direct construction, subclassing, or "
"lifecycle tests. Install the corresponding optional dependency on the "
"driver and workers before importing a connector module."
msgstr ""
"大多数应用应使用模块级 ``ray.klein.read_*`` 函数和 :class:`~ray.klein.DataStream` "
"写入器方法。以下类是公共扩展契约，可用于直接构造、子类化或生命周期测试。导入连接器模块之前，请在驱动程序和工作节点上安装相应的可选依赖。"

msgid "Kafka"
msgstr "Kafka"

msgid "Continuously consume Kafka with deterministic partition ownership."
msgstr "以确定性的分区所有权持续消费 Kafka。"

msgid ""
"Records use the same raw-byte schema as ``ray.data.read_kafka``. Each "
"subtask manually owns a deterministic subset of the discovered topic "
"partitions, so a source restart can seek to the next offsets captured in "
"a Klein checkpoint. Kafka group offsets are committed only after the "
"matching checkpoint becomes durable."
msgstr ""
"记录使用与 ``ray.data.read_kafka`` "
"相同的原始字节模式。每个子任务手动拥有所发现主题分区的一个确定性子集，因此源重启时可以定位到 Klein "
"检查点中捕获的下一偏移量。只有匹配的检查点持久化后，才会提交 Kafka 消费组偏移量。"

msgid "Ask a running source loop to return without releasing resources."
msgstr "请求正在运行的源循环返回，但不释放资源。"

msgid ""
"Implementations should set an event or flag observed by :meth:`run`. "
"Resource cleanup belongs in ``Function.close`` and is invoked once by the"
" task lifecycle after the source loop has stopped."
msgstr ""
"实现应设置一个由 :meth:`run` 观察的事件或标志。资源清理属于 "
"``Function.close``，并在源循环停止后由任务生命周期调用一次。"

msgid "Return type"
msgstr "返回类型"

msgid "Release the consumer after the source loop has stopped."
msgstr "在源循环停止后释放消费者。"

msgid "Notify the source that a checkpoint is durably complete."
msgstr "通知源某个检查点已经持久化完成。"

msgid ""
"Delivery is at least once across coordinator recovery, so implementations"
" must use ``checkpoint_id`` as an idempotency key."
msgstr "协调器恢复期间至少会投递一次，因此实现必须将 ``checkpoint_id`` 用作幂等键。"

msgid "Initialize the function before processing starts."
msgstr "开始处理前初始化函数。"

msgid "Restore state previously returned by :meth:`snapshot_state`."
msgstr "恢复此前由 :meth:`snapshot_state` 返回的状态。"

msgid ""
"The main loop for fetching data from DataSource. It will be triggered "
"with a separate thread."
msgstr "从 DataSource 获取数据的主循环。它将在独立线程中触发。"

msgid "Return this source subtask's opaque state at ``checkpoint_id``."
msgstr "返回此源子任务在 ``checkpoint_id`` 处的不透明状态。"

msgid ""
"The value must be pickleable. Sources should normally capture the "
"position of the next record to read and advance that position before "
"calling ``SourceContext.collect`` so a barrier emitted by that call "
"observes the matching state."
msgstr ""
"该值必须可被 pickle。源通常应捕获下一条待读记录的位置，并在调用 ``SourceContext.collect`` "
"前推进该位置，使该调用发出的屏障能够观察到匹配的状态。"

msgid "Produce streaming records to Kafka and flush them at checkpoints."
msgstr "向 Kafka 生成流式记录，并在检查点处刷新。"

msgid ""
"A successful flush means every record before the aligned checkpoint has a"
" delivery acknowledgement from Kafka. Replaying an unacknowledged input "
"can produce duplicates, so the sink provides at-least-once rather than "
"exactly-once delivery."
msgstr "刷新成功表示对齐检查点之前的每条记录都已收到 Kafka 的交付确认。重放未确认的输入可能产生重复，因此该接收器提供至少一次而非恰好一次交付。"

msgid "Release resources after processing stops."
msgstr "处理停止后释放资源。"

msgid "Flush buffered records to the external system, if applicable."
msgstr "如适用，将缓冲记录刷新到外部系统。"

msgid ""
"Writes the given value to the sink. This function is called for every "
"record. The function is mutually exclusive with function 'flush'"
msgstr "将给定值写入 sink。每条记录都会调用此函数；此函数与函数 'flush' 互斥。"

msgid "Apache RocketMQ"
msgstr "Apache RocketMQ"

msgid "Continuously consume one Apache RocketMQ topic."
msgstr "持续消费一个 Apache RocketMQ 主题。"

msgid ""
"``rocketmq-client-python`` exposes a callback-based PushConsumer rather "
"than a seekable pull consumer. The callback copies the native message "
"into a bounded Python queue and waits until the source thread has emitted"
" it downstream before returning ``CONSUME_SUCCESS``. RocketMQ consumer-"
"group progress is therefore the recovery boundary; the opaque Klein "
"checkpoint state records only the connector-state version."
msgstr ""
"``rocketmq-client-python`` 公开的是基于回调的 "
"PushConsumer，而不是可定位的拉取消费者。回调会将原生消息复制到有界 Python 队列中，并等待源线程将其发送到下游，然后才返回 "
"``CONSUME_SUCCESS``。因此，RocketMQ 消费组进度就是恢复边界；不透明的 Klein 检查点状态只记录连接器状态版本。"

msgid "Filesystem"
msgstr "文件系统"

msgid "Checkpoint-transactional file sink for local and object filesystems."
msgstr "面向本地文件系统和对象文件系统的检查点事务型文件接收器。"

msgid "Discard writer-local data that has not reached ``prepare_commit``."
msgstr "丢弃尚未到达 ``prepare_commit`` 的 writer 本地数据。"

msgid "Close the current transaction and return its committable."
msgstr "关闭当前事务并返回其 committable。"

msgid ""
"``None`` means the transaction contains no output. The writer must begin "
"a fresh transaction before accepting the next record."
msgstr "``None`` 表示事务不包含输出。writer 必须先开始一个新事务，才能接受下一条记录。"

msgid "Apache Iceberg"
msgstr "Apache Iceberg"

msgid "Checkpoint-transactional append sink for an existing Iceberg table."
msgstr "面向现有 Iceberg 表的检查点事务型追加接收器。"

msgid "Database API"
msgstr "数据库 API"

msgid "Write streaming records through a DB-API 2.0 ``executemany`` call."
msgstr "通过 DB-API 2.0 ``executemany`` 调用写入流式记录。"

msgid ""
"Full batches and checkpoint flushes are committed independently. A commit"
" can therefore become visible before its corresponding Klein checkpoint "
"is durable, so recovery provides at-least-once delivery."
msgstr "完整批次和检查点刷新会独立提交。因此，一次提交可能在对应的 Klein 检查点持久化之前可见，所以恢复提供至少一次交付。"

msgid "Console"
msgstr "控制台"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`../connectors/index` for installation, schemas, complete option"
" tables, execution-mode support, delivery guarantees, and operational "
"guidance."
msgstr "有关安装、模式、完整选项表、执行模式支持、交付保证和运维指南，请参阅 :doc:`../connectors/index`。"

msgid "Pipeline configuration and compatibility API"
msgstr "管道配置与兼容性 API"

msgid ""
"Application code should build streams with module-level ``from_*`` and "
"``read_*`` functions, attach terminal sinks, and call ``execute(\"job-"
"name\")`` after the complete graph has been registered. ``KleinContext`` "
"remains for advanced isolation; selective sink roots are documented in "
"the advanced section of :doc:`../job-lifecycle`."
msgstr ""
"应用代码应使用模块级 ``from_*`` 和 ``read_*`` 函数构建流、附加终端接收器，并在完整计算图注册完毕后调用 "
"``execute(\"job-name\")``。``KleinContext`` 仍用于高级隔离；选择性 sink 根用法见 "
":doc:`../job-lifecycle` 的高级章节。"

msgid "Advanced configuration and graph owner for one isolated pipeline."
msgstr "单个隔离管道的高级配置和图所有者。"

msgid ""
"Ordinary applications use the module-level source, terminal, and "
":func:`execute` APIs. Direct construction remains available when one "
"process must build explicitly isolated pipelines."
msgstr "普通应用使用模块级源、终端和 :func:`execute` API。当一个进程必须构建显式隔离的管道时，仍可直接构造。"

