msgid "Exceptions and failure handling"
msgstr "异常与故障处理"

msgid ""
"Klein validates graph and connector arguments early with standard Python "
"exceptions. Distributed runtime failures are retained by the job and "
"surfaced through :class:`~ray.klein.JobHandle`, the CLI, logs, and state "
"snapshots."
msgstr ""
"Klein 会尽早使用标准 Python 异常验证图和连接器参数。分布式运行时故障由作业保留，并通过 "
":class:`~ray.klein.JobHandle`、CLI、日志和状态快照呈现。"

msgid "Public exception types"
msgstr "公共异常类型"

msgid "Base exception for Klein for Ray failures."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 故障的基础异常。"

msgid "Raised when a Klein SQL query or its table bindings are invalid."
msgstr "Klein SQL 查询或其表绑定无效时引发。"

msgid ""
"``RayDataAPIError`` is documented with the :doc:`Ray Data adapter "
"<ray_data>` because it reports dynamic factory and Dataset-method "
"contract violations."
msgstr ""
"``RayDataAPIError`` 与 :doc:`Ray Data 适配器 <ray_data>` 一同记录，因为它报告动态工厂和 "
"Dataset 方法的契约违规。"

msgid "Raised when a state update loses an optimistic-version race."
msgstr "状态更新在乐观版本竞争中失败时引发。"

msgid "Common exception families"
msgstr "常见异常系列"

msgid "``TypeError``"
msgstr "``TypeError``"

msgid ""
"An argument or user record has the wrong Python type. Correct the graph, "
"connector input, state descriptor, or configuration value before "
"retrying."
msgstr "参数或用户记录使用了错误的 Python 类型。请先修正图、连接器输入、状态描述符或配置值，再重试。"

msgid "``ValueError``"
msgstr "``ValueError``"

msgid ""
"A value is malformed, outside its allowed range, or represents an "
"unsupported combination. SQL planning uses the more specific "
":class:`~ray.klein.SQLQueryError`, which is also a ``ValueError``."
msgstr ""
"值的格式错误、超出允许范围或表示不受支持的组合。SQL 规划使用更具体的 "
":class:`~ray.klein.SQLQueryError`，它也是 ``ValueError``。"

msgid "``ModuleNotFoundError``"
msgstr "``ModuleNotFoundError``"

msgid ""
"An optional integration is missing. Install the connector extra in the "
"driver and every eligible worker; do not catch this and continue with a "
"partially configured graph."
msgstr "缺少可选集成。请在驱动程序和每个符合条件的工作节点中安装连接器额外依赖；不要捕获该异常后继续运行仅配置了一部分的图。"

msgid "``RayDataAPIError``"
msgstr "``RayDataAPIError``"

msgid ""
"A dynamic ``ray.klein.read_*`` or ``stream.data`` operation is "
"unavailable or used in the wrong adapter category for the installed Ray "
"version."
msgstr ""
"对于已安装的 Ray 版本，动态 ``ray.klein.read_*`` 或 ``stream.data`` "
"操作不可用，或者被用在错误的适配器类别中。"

msgid "``StateConflictError``"
msgstr "``StateConflictError``"

msgid ""
"A managed-state declaration conflicts with an existing state name or "
"contract. Treat this as an application compatibility error rather than a "
"transient worker failure."
msgstr "托管状态声明与现有状态名称或契约冲突。应将其视为应用兼容性错误，而不是暂时的工作节点故障。"

msgid "``KleinError``"
msgstr "``KleinError``"

msgid ""
"A submitted job reached a failure boundary. ``LiveJobHandle.wait()`` "
"raises this with the retained job failure detail. The collection-specific"
" ``get()`` path does not perform that explicit failed-status check; call "
"``wait()`` or inspect ``status`` when failure propagation matters."
msgstr ""
"已提交的作业到达失败边界。``LiveJobHandle.wait()`` 会抛出此异常，并附带保留的作业失败详情。面向收集的 "
"``get()`` 路径不会执行该显式失败状态检查；当需要传播失败时，请调用 ``wait()`` 或检查 ``status``。"

msgid "``TimeoutError``"
msgstr "``TimeoutError``"

msgid ""
"A client wait, deployment, data-plane drain, or control operation "
"exceeded its time budget. A control timeout does not prove the remote "
"operation was rolled back; refresh the job snapshot before retrying."
msgstr "客户端等待、部署、数据平面排空或控制操作超出时间预算。控制超时并不能证明远程操作已经回滚；重试前请刷新作业快照。"

msgid "``FileNotFoundError`` or ``OSError``"
msgstr "``FileNotFoundError`` 或 ``OSError``"

msgid ""
"A checkpoint object, local dependency, filesystem path, or external "
"resource is unavailable. Verify the URI, credentials, shared visibility, "
"and checkpoint completion marker before choosing another restore point."
msgstr "检查点对象、本地依赖、文件系统路径或外部资源不可用。选择其他恢复点之前，请验证 URI、凭据、共享可见性和检查点完成标记。"

msgid "Retry guidance"
msgstr "重试指南"

msgid ""
"Do not retry every exception at the driver. Native streaming workers and "
"the JobManager already apply the configured restart policy to eligible "
"task failures. Repeated driver submissions can create another job "
"namespace or duplicate external effects."
msgstr ""
"不要在驱动程序中重试每一个异常。原生流处理工作节点和 JobManager "
"已经对符合条件的任务故障应用配置的重启策略。重复从驱动程序提交可能创建另一个作业命名空间，或造成重复的外部副作用。"

msgid ""
"Correct ``TypeError``, ``ValueError``, ``SQLQueryError``, "
"``RayDataAPIError``, and missing-dependency failures in code or "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"请在代码或配置中修正 "
"``TypeError``、``ValueError``、``SQLQueryError``、``RayDataAPIError`` "
"和缺少依赖的故障。"

msgid ""
"For a live-job ``KleinError``, inspect the retained failure, task status,"
" and latest completed checkpoint before resubmission."
msgstr "对于实时作业的 ``KleinError``，请在重新提交前检查保留的故障、任务状态和最新完成的检查点。"

msgid ""
"After a client-side timeout from cancellation or rescaling, query status "
"before sending another control request."
msgstr "取消或伸缩发生客户端侧超时后，请先查询状态，再发送另一控制请求。"

msgid ""
"Retry an external connector error only when its connector guide defines "
"the source-position or sink-idempotency boundary."
msgstr "仅当相应连接器指南定义了源位置或接收器幂等性边界时，才重试外部连接器错误。"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`../troubleshooting` for symptom-oriented diagnosis and :doc"
":`../delivery-semantics` for the duplicate/loss consequences of recovery."
msgstr ""
"有关面向症状的诊断，请参阅 :doc:`../troubleshooting`；有关恢复造成的重复/丢失后果，请参阅 :doc"
":`../delivery-semantics`。"

msgid "Message format API"
msgstr "消息格式 API"

msgid "Canal JSON"
msgstr "Canal JSON"

msgid "Decode one Canal ``FlatMessage`` JSON value."
msgstr "解码一个 Canal ``FlatMessage`` JSON 值。"

msgid ""
"Canal represents row values as strings (or ``null``); this decoder keeps "
"those values unchanged. UPDATE ``old`` entries contain only the columns "
"that changed, so they are overlaid on the corresponding full ``data`` row"
" to reconstruct the before image."
msgstr ""
"Canal 将行值表示为字符串（或 ``null``）；该解码器保持这些值不变。UPDATE 的 ``old`` "
"条目只包含发生变化的列，因此会将它们覆盖到相应的完整 ``data`` 行上，以重建变更前镜像。"

msgid ""
"The decoder preserves Canal's string-or-null column representation and "
"returns zero or more :class:`~ray.klein.ChangelogRow` values. See "
":doc:`../connectors/canal` for the input envelope, metadata columns, DDL "
"policy, ordering, and checkpoint behavior."
msgstr ""
"该解码器保留 Canal 的字符串或 null 列表示，并返回零个或多个 :class:`~ray.klein.ChangelogRow` "
"值。有关输入信封、元数据列、DDL 策略、顺序和检查点行为，请参阅 :doc:`../connectors/canal`。"

msgid "Job lifecycle API"
msgstr "作业生命周期 API"

msgid ""
"``execute()`` returns a :class:`JobHandle`. Bounded jobs may already be "
"complete when the handle is returned; streaming jobs remain live until "
"the source finishes, the job fails, or the caller cancels it. Application"
" code should program against ``JobHandle`` rather than its concrete "
"implementation."
msgstr ""
"``execute()`` 返回 "
":class:`JobHandle`。返回句柄时，有界作业可能已经完成；流式作业则会一直运行，直到源结束、作业失败或调用方取消作业。应用代码应面向"
" ``JobHandle`` 编程，而不应依赖其具体实现。"

msgid "The result of :meth:`JobClient.execute` — a job to observe and control."
msgstr ":meth:`JobClient.execute` 的结果——一个可观测、可控制的作业。"

msgid ""
"A handle is the *running (or finished) job*, never the builder. The two "
"concrete forms — :class:`LiveJobHandle` (a submitted streaming job backed"
" by a JobManager actor) and :class:`CompletedJobHandle` (an already-"
"finished batch / compile-only run with an in-memory result) — are "
"siblings, so each only implements what is true for it."
msgstr ""
"句柄表示的是 *正在运行（或已经结束）的作业* ，绝不是构建器。两种具体形式—— :class:`LiveJobHandle` （由 "
"JobManager actor 支持的已提交流式作业）和 :class:`CompletedJobHandle` "
"（带内存结果、已经完成的批处理或仅编译运行）——互为同级类型，因此各自只实现对自身成立的能力。"

msgid "Cancel the job."
msgstr "取消作业。"

msgid "Block and return the result of one result-producing terminal."
msgstr "阻塞并返回单个产生结果的终端操作的结果。"

msgid ""
"Use :meth:`wait` for jobs containing side-effect terminals or multiple "
"sinks. A collecting ``take``/``take_all`` terminal must execute alone."
msgstr ""
"对于包含副作用终端操作或多个 sink 的作业，请使用 :meth:`wait`。收集型 ``take``/``take_all`` "
"终端操作必须单独执行。"

msgid "Per-job Ray namespace."
msgstr "每个作业独立的 Ray 命名空间。"

msgid "Current job status."
msgstr "当前作业状态。"

msgid "Block until the job reaches a terminal state."
msgstr "阻塞直到作业进入终止状态。"

msgid "Lifecycle states exposed by a Klein job handle."
msgstr "Klein 作业句柄公开的生命周期状态。"

msgid "Typical control flow"
msgstr "典型控制流程"

msgid ""
"``wait()`` blocks until a terminal state and is the normal choice for "
"jobs with one or more side-effect sinks. ``get()`` is for one result-"
"producing terminal; ``take()`` or ``take_all()`` must be executed alone. "
"``cancel(timeout=...)`` requests a cooperative stop and returns whether "
"cancellation completed inside the time budget. A live handle's "
"``namespace`` is the Ray namespace accepted by the ``ray-klein status``, "
"``attach``, and ``stop`` commands."
msgstr ""
"``wait()`` 会阻塞到终止状态，是包含一个或多个副作用 sink 的作业的常规选择。``get()`` 用于单个产生结果的终端操作；"
"``take()`` 或 ``take_all()`` 必须单独执行。``cancel(timeout=...)`` 请求协作式停止，并返回取消是否在时间预算内完成。"
"实时句柄的 ``namespace`` 是 ``ray-klein status``、``attach`` 和 ``stop`` 命令接受的 Ray 命名空间。"

msgid "Metrics API"
msgstr "指标 API"

msgid ""
"User functions receive a :class:`MetricGroup` through their runtime "
"context. Lifecycle sources and sinks receive that context in ``open()``; "
"a callable transform class can request a constructor keyword named "
"``runtime_context``. Register metrics once during worker initialization "
"and update the returned task-local handle while processing. Reusing one "
"name with a different kind, description, histogram boundary set, or label"
" set raises ``ValueError``."
msgstr ""
"用户函数通过运行时上下文接收 :class:`MetricGroup`。生命周期源和 sink 在 ``open()`` 中接收该上下文；可调用转换类可以请求名为 "
"``runtime_context`` 的构造函数关键字参数。请在 worker 初始化期间只注册一次指标，并在处理期间更新返回的任务本地句柄。若以不同的种类、"
"描述、直方图边界集合或标签集合复用同一名称，将引发 ``ValueError``。"

msgid "A scope that adds stable labels and a prefix to Ray metrics."
msgstr "为 Ray 指标添加稳定标签和前缀的作用域。"

msgid "Create a child metric group."
msgstr "创建子指标组。"

msgid "Return all inherited labels."
msgstr "返回所有继承的标签。"

msgid "Register a user-defined counter."
msgstr "注册用户定义的 counter。"

msgid "Register a user-defined gauge."
msgstr "注册用户定义的 gauge。"

msgid "Register a user-defined histogram."
msgstr "注册用户定义的 histogram。"

msgid "Return the fully qualified Ray metric name."
msgstr "返回完全限定的 Ray 指标名称。"

msgid "Return the local group name."
msgstr "返回本地组名称。"

msgid "Metric metadata exposed by Ray."
msgstr "Ray 公开的指标元数据。"

msgid "Task-local readable mirror; Ray's metric handle is write-only."
msgstr "任务本地的可读镜像；Ray 的指标句柄仅支持写入。"

msgid "Reset a data-driven gauge so its last sample is not read as live data."
msgstr "重置数据驱动的 gauge，避免将其最后一个样本误读为实时数据。"

msgid "Observe elapsed monotonic time and return the duration in milliseconds."
msgstr "观测经过的单调时间，并返回以毫秒为单位的时长。"

msgid "Context manager for synchronous operations measured in milliseconds."
msgstr "用于以毫秒计量同步操作的上下文管理器。"

msgid "An enumeration."
msgstr "一个枚举。"

msgid "The stable contract of one built-in metric."
msgstr "一个内置指标的稳定契约。"

msgid ""
"Metric names deliberately omit Prometheus suffixes such as ``_total``. "
"Ray's exporter adds those suffixes for counters."
msgstr "指标名称有意省略 ``_total`` 等 Prometheus 后缀。Ray 导出器会为计数器添加这些后缀。"

msgid ""
"``JobMetricGroup``, ``TaskMetricGroup``, and ``OperatorMetricGroup`` are "
"runtime-owned scopes. Application code should use the group supplied by "
"the runtime instead of constructing those classes. ``KleinMetrics`` is "
"the canonical built-in catalog used by instrumentation and tests."
msgstr ""
"``JobMetricGroup``、``TaskMetricGroup`` 和 ``OperatorMetricGroup`` "
"是运行时拥有的作用域。应用代码应使用运行时提供的组，而不是构造这些类。``KleinMetrics`` 是插桩和测试使用的规范内置目录。"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`../observability` for prefixes, labels, built-in metric names, "
"Prometheus queries, cardinality rules, and interpretation."
msgstr "有关前缀、标签、内置指标名称、Prometheus 查询、基数规则和解读，请参阅 :doc:`../observability`。"

msgid "Observability and control API"
msgstr "可观测性与控制 API"

msgid ""
"The state API returns JSON-safe dictionaries intended for automation and "
"dashboard adapters. Call ``ray.init(address=\"auto\")`` before querying a"
" remote cluster."
msgstr ""
"状态 API 返回适用于自动化和 Dashboard 适配器的 JSON 安全字典。查询远程集群前，请调用 "
"``ray.init(address=\"auto\")``。"

msgid ":py:obj:`list_job_snapshots <ray.klein.list_job_snapshots>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`list_job_snapshots <ray.klein.list_job_snapshots>`"

msgid "Return current and retained Klein job snapshots from this Ray cluster."
msgstr "返回此 Ray 集群中当前及保留的 Klein 作业快照。"

msgid ":py:obj:`get_job_snapshot <ray.klein.get_job_snapshot>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`get_job_snapshot <ray.klein.get_job_snapshot>`"

msgid "Return one job snapshot, or ``None`` when the job is unknown."
msgstr "返回一个作业快照；作业未知时返回 ``None``。"

msgid ":py:obj:`rescale_operator <ray.klein.rescale_operator>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`rescale_operator <ray.klein.rescale_operator>`"

msgid "Change one published operator's parallelism."
msgstr "更改一个已发布算子的并行度。"

msgid ":py:obj:`cancel_job <ray.klein.cancel_job>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`cancel_job <ray.klein.cancel_job>`"

msgid "Cancel one published job by ID and wait for the state actor response."
msgstr "按 ID 取消一个已发布作业，并等待状态 actor 响应。"

msgid ":py:obj:`configure_logging <ray.klein.configure_logging>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`configure_logging <ray.klein.configure_logging>`"

msgid "Configure Klein's logger without modifying application/root handlers."
msgstr "配置 Klein 日志记录器，而不修改应用或根处理器。"

msgid ""
"``list_job_snapshots()`` returns current jobs plus retained terminal "
"history. ``get_job_snapshot(job_id)`` returns one snapshot or ``None``. "
"``rescale_operator(job_id, operator_id, parallelism, timeout=60)`` "
"performs a local, barrier-aligned parallelism change when the operator "
"supports it and returns a JSON-safe operation result whose status is "
"``COMPLETED``, ``NOOP``, ``REJECTED``, or ``FAILED``. The first version "
"does not resize source operators, transactional sinks, or collecting "
"sinks. Multiple source operators and source subtasks are coordinated "
"within checkpoint domains. See :doc:`../operator-rescaling` for "
"prerequisites, result handling, state migration, and the stabilization "
"checkpoint. ``cancel_job(job_id, timeout=60)`` addresses a published job "
"by job ID, while the CLI ``stop`` command addresses its Ray namespace."
msgstr ""
"``list_job_snapshots()`` 返回当前作业及保留的终止历史。``get_job_snapshot(job_id)`` "
"返回一个快照，未知时返回 ``None``。``rescale_operator(job_id, operator_id, "
"parallelism, timeout=60)`` 在算子支持时执行本地、屏障对齐的并行度变更，并返回 JSON 安全的操作结果，其状态为 "
"``COMPLETED``、``NOOP``、``REJECTED`` 或 ``FAILED``。首个版本不会调整源算子、事务型 sink "
"或收集型 sink。多个源算子和源子任务会在各自的检查点域内协调。有关前置条件、结果处理、状态迁移和稳定化检查点，请参阅 :doc"
":`../operator-rescaling`。``cancel_job(job_id, timeout=60)`` 按作业 ID "
"定位已发布作业，而 CLI 的 ``stop`` 命令按其 Ray 命名空间定位。"

msgid "Snapshot keys"
msgstr "快照字段"

msgid ""
"Consumers must tolerate additional keys in future versions. Current "
"snapshots contain job identity and status, namespace, operator topology "
"and task status, throughput and backpressure summaries, checkpoint "
"history, redacted configuration, failure details, and ``dashboard_stale``"
" when the state actor returns its last good cached value."
msgstr ""
"使用方必须容许未来版本增加字段。当前快照包含作业标识与状态、命名空间、算子拓扑与任务状态、吞吐量与背压摘要、检查点历史、脱敏配置、失败详情；当状态"
" actor 返回最近一次有效缓存值时，还包含 ``dashboard_stale``。"

msgid ""
"Operator rows expose interval averages as ``busy_percent`` and "
"``backpressure_percent``. ``max_busy_percent`` and "
"``max_backpressure_percent`` contain the hottest subtask values used to "
"color the Dashboard job graph."
msgstr ""
"算子行以 ``busy_percent`` 和 ``backpressure_percent`` "
"公开区间平均值。``max_busy_percent`` 和 ``max_backpressure_percent`` "
"包含最繁忙子任务的值，用于为 Dashboard 作业图着色。"

msgid ""
"The API does not make terminal history durable. Checkpoint storage and "
"state snapshots have separate lifecycles; see :doc:`../observability`."
msgstr "此 API 不会持久化终止历史。检查点存储与状态快照具有相互独立的生命周期；请参阅 :doc:`../observability`。"

msgid "Partitioning API"
msgstr "分区 API"

msgid ""
"Prefer the convenience methods on :class:`ray.klein.DataStream`. "
"Implement a custom partitioner only when the built-in forward, round-"
"robin, rescale, broadcast, key, and adaptive strategies do not express "
"the required topology."
msgstr ""
"优先使用 :class:`ray.klein.DataStream` 上的便捷方法。只有当内置的 forward、round-"
"robin、rescale、broadcast、key 和 adaptive 策略无法表达所需拓扑时，才实现自定义分区器。"

msgid ":py:obj:`Partitioner <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.Partitioner>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`Partitioner <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.Partitioner>`"

msgid "Task-local data routing policy."
msgstr "任务本地的数据路由策略。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`ForwardPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ForwardPartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`ForwardPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ForwardPartitioner>`"

msgid ""
"Default partition for operator if the operator can be chained with "
"succeeding operators."
msgstr "当算子可与后续算子链接时使用的默认分区方式。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`RoundRobinPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.RoundRobinPartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`RoundRobinPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.RoundRobinPartitioner>`"

msgid "Partition record to downstream tasks in a round-robin matter."
msgstr "以轮询方式将记录分配给下游任务。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`RescalePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.RescalePartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`RescalePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.RescalePartitioner>`"

msgid "Worker-pool partitioner over a statically-assigned subset of downstreams."
msgstr "在静态分配的下游子集上工作的 worker pool 分区器。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`BroadcastPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.BroadcastPartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`BroadcastPartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.BroadcastPartitioner>`"

msgid "Broadcast the record to all downstream partitions."
msgstr "将记录广播到所有下游分区。"

msgid ":py:obj:`KeyPartitioner <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.KeyPartitioner>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`KeyPartitioner <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.KeyPartitioner>`"

msgid "Partition the record by the key."
msgstr "按键对记录进行分区。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`AdaptivePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.AdaptivePartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`AdaptivePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.AdaptivePartitioner>`"

msgid "Round-robin initial routing with a full eligible-worker retry ring."
msgstr "以轮询方式进行初始路由，并提供完整的合格 worker 重试环。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`SimplePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.SimplePartitioner>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`SimplePartitioner "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.SimplePartitioner>`"

msgid "Wrap a python function as subclass of :class:`Partition`"
msgstr "将 Python 函数包装为 :class:`Partition` 的子类。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`WorkerPoolDispatcher "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.WorkerPoolDispatcher>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`WorkerPoolDispatcher "
"<ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.WorkerPoolDispatcher>`"

msgid "Backpressure-driven round-robin over a fixed set of downstream tasks."
msgstr "在固定下游任务集合上进行背压驱动的轮询。"

msgid ":py:obj:`ChannelPattern <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ChannelPattern>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`ChannelPattern <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ChannelPattern>`"

msgid ":py:obj:`ChannelTopology <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ChannelTopology>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`ChannelTopology <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.ChannelTopology>`"

msgid "Pure mapping from one upstream subtask to its downstream channels."
msgstr "从一个上游子任务到其下游通道的纯映射。"

msgid ":py:obj:`PartitionerSpec <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.PartitionerSpec>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`PartitionerSpec <ray.klein.runtime.partitioning.PartitionerSpec>`"

msgid "Picklable constructor recipe stored on logical and physical edges."
msgstr "存储在逻辑边和物理边上的可 pickle 构造配方。"

msgid ""
"A custom ``Partitioner`` passed to ``DataStream.partition_by`` must "
"produce an immutable ``PartitionerSpec`` through ``to_spec()``. The spec,"
" rather than a driver-owned mutable partitioner instance, is serialized "
"into the execution graph and reconstructed per worker."
msgstr ""
"传给 ``DataStream.partition_by`` 的自定义 ``Partitioner`` 必须通过 ``to_spec()`` "
"生成不可变的 ``PartitionerSpec``。序列化进执行图并在每个 worker 上重建的是该 spec，而不是由 driver "
"持有的可变分区器实例。"

msgid ""
"Physical/control topology belongs to :attr:`topology`; retry candidates "
"are decided while still on the operator thread and are immutable "
"afterwards. The send layer therefore never calls back into a mutable "
"partitioner."
msgstr "物理和控制拓扑归 :attr:`topology` 所有；重试候选项仍在算子线程中时便已决定，此后保持不可变。因此，发送层绝不会回调可变分区器。"

msgid "Return the downstream partition indices for one record."
msgstr "返回一条记录对应的下游分区索引。"

msgid "Route a *columnar* batch without exploding it into per-row records."
msgstr "路由*列式*批次，而不将其拆成逐行记录。"

msgid ""
"Returns ``(target_index, row_indices)`` pairs. ``row_indices is None`` is"
" a fast-path meaning \"the WHOLE batch goes to this target\" (no slicing)"
" — used by content-independent partitioners (forward / broadcast / round-"
"robin / worker-pool), where routing doesn't depend on row values, so the "
"batch travels as one unit and balancing granularity is per-batch."
msgstr ""
"返回 ``(target_index, row_indices)`` 对。``row_indices is None`` "
"是表示“整个批次都发送到该目标”（不切片）的快速路径，供与内容无关的分区器（forward / broadcast / round-robin /"
" worker-pool）使用；这些分区器的路由不依赖行值，因此批次作为一个整体传输，负载均衡粒度为每批次。"

msgid ""
"Key/hash partitioning overrides this to group rows by key and return one "
"``(target_index, [row...])`` pair per distinct target (see "
"KeyPartitioner)."
msgstr ""
"键/哈希分区会重写此方法，以按键对行分组，并为每个不同目标返回一个 ``(target_index, [row...])`` 对（参见 "
"KeyPartitioner）。"

msgid ""
"Default implementation defers to :meth:`partition` (called once with the "
"batch record, content ignored by these partitioners) and ships the whole "
"batch to each returned target."
msgstr "默认实现委托给 :meth:`partition` （以批记录调用一次，这些分区器会忽略内容），并将整个批次发送到每个返回的目标。"

msgid "Return the finite retry ring, starting with ``initial_target``."
msgstr "返回从 ``initial_target`` 开始的有限重试环。"

msgid ""
"The default preserves affinity. Load-balancing partitioners override it "
"with their static eligible channel ring. The RecordRouter validates and "
"freezes this decision before it crosses from the operator thread to the "
"emit loop."
msgstr "默认实现保持亲和性。负载均衡分区器会用其静态合格通道环重写此行为。RecordRouter 会在该决定从算子线程跨入发出循环前对其进行验证并冻结。"

msgid "Return an immutable recipe containing every constructor argument."
msgstr "返回包含所有构造函数参数的不可变配方。"

msgid "Ray Data adapter API"
msgstr "Ray Data 适配器 API"

msgid "Dynamic namespace for public ``ray.data`` Dataset factories."
msgstr "公共 ``ray.data`` Dataset 工厂的动态命名空间。"

msgid "Dynamic namespace for public ``ray.data.Dataset`` operations."
msgstr "公共 ``ray.data.Dataset`` 操作的动态命名空间。"

msgid "How a Ray ``Dataset`` method participates in a Klein graph."
msgstr "Ray ``Dataset`` 方法参与 Klein 图的方式。"

msgid "Raised when a dynamic Ray Data call violates its Klein contract."
msgstr "动态 Ray Data 调用违反 Klein 契约时引发。"

msgid "Advanced discovery contracts"
msgstr "高级发现契约"

msgid ""
"The following functions support adapters that need to inspect the public "
"API of the installed compatible Ray version. Ordinary graph code should "
"prefer ``name in ctx.data.available`` and ``name in "
"stream.data.available``."
msgstr ""
"以下函数支持需要检查已安装兼容 Ray 版本公共 API 的适配器。普通计算图代码应优先使用 ``name in ctx.data.available`` "
"和 ``name in stream.data.available``。"

msgid ""
