"extractors, and an optional immutable sink configuration::"
msgstr "``DataStream.write_redis`` 接受一个连接对象、键和值提取器，以及可选的不可变 sink 配置::"

msgid ""
"Strings are replaced with ``SET``. Hashes, lists, and sets are replaced "
"in a transaction using ``DEL`` followed by ``HSET``, ``RPUSH``, or "
"``SADD``. This makes retrying a batch idempotent and preserves list "
"order."
msgstr ""
"字符串使用 ``SET`` 替换。哈希、列表和集合在事务中先执行 ``DEL``，再执行 ``HSET``、``RPUSH`` 或 "
"``SADD`` 来替换。这使批次重试具有幂等性，并能保留列表顺序。"

msgid "Resource plan API"
msgstr "资源计划 API"

msgid ""
"``explain()`` returns the JSON representation of a :class:`ResourcePlan`."
" Applications normally set resources on sources, transforms, and sinks; "
"the classes below support offline inspection and validated override "
"files."
msgstr ""
"``explain()`` 返回 :class:`ResourcePlan` 的 JSON "
"表示。应用通常在源、转换和接收器上设置资源；以下类支持离线检查和经过验证的覆盖文件。"

msgid "Serializable resource overrides for a stream graph."
msgstr "流图的可序列化资源覆盖。"

msgid "Replace one node through its validated immutable contract."
msgstr "通过经过验证的不可变契约替换一个节点。"

msgid ""
"Only execution-tuning fields may change; graph identity stays fixed. "
"Passing ``None`` explicitly clears an existing override."
msgstr "只有执行调优字段可以更改；图身份保持不变。显式传入 ``None`` 会清除现有覆盖。"

msgid "Validated resource settings for one stream graph node."
msgstr "一个流图节点经过验证的资源设置。"

msgid "Directed edge in a serialized resource plan."
msgstr "序列化资源计划中的有向边。"

msgid ""
"Set ``RAY_KLEIN_RESOURCE_PLAN_PERSIST_PATH`` to write the compiled plan "
"and ``RAY_KLEIN_RESOURCE_PLAN_LOAD_PATH`` to apply a compatible plan "
"during submission. A loaded plan must contain the same node keys as the "
"compiled graph; only CPU, GPU, concurrency, batch-size, and asynchronous-"
"buffer fields are mutable through "
":meth:`~ray.klein.api.resource_plan.ResourcePlan.update_node`."
msgstr ""
"设置 ``RAY_KLEIN_RESOURCE_PLAN_PERSIST_PATH`` 可写入编译后的计划，设置 "
"``RAY_KLEIN_RESOURCE_PLAN_LOAD_PATH`` 可在提交期间应用兼容计划。加载的计划必须包含与编译图相同的节点键；只有"
" CPU、GPU、并发度、批大小和异步缓冲区字段可通过 "
":meth:`~ray.klein.api.resource_plan.ResourcePlan.update_node` 修改。"

msgid ""
"Plan files are deployment inputs, not state snapshots. They contain no "
"source position or managed state and cannot restore a job."
msgstr "计划文件是部署输入，不是状态快照。它们不包含源位置或托管状态，无法恢复作业。"

msgid "User-function runtime API"
msgstr "用户函数运行时 API"

msgid ""
"Callable classes can request a ``runtime_context`` constructor argument. "
"The context exposes the physical task identity, effective configuration, "
"batching settings, and a metric group. Keep it on the worker; it is not a"
" serializable driver-side job handle."
msgstr ""
"可调用类可以请求 ``runtime_context`` 构造函数参数。该上下文公开物理任务标识、有效配置、批处理设置和指标组。请将它保留在 "
"worker 上；它不是可序列化的 driver 端作业句柄。"

msgid "Read-only execution context handed to a user function's ``open()``."
msgstr "传给用户函数 ``open()`` 的只读执行上下文。"

msgid ""
"Common capabilities are available in both stream and batch execution; "
"stream-only checkpoint capabilities live on "
":class:`StreamRuntimeContext`."
msgstr "流处理和批处理执行均提供通用能力；仅限流处理的检查点能力位于 :class:`StreamRuntimeContext`。"

msgid "The config with which the parallel task runs."
msgstr "并行任务运行时使用的配置。"

msgid "Stable identifier used to scope state and observability."
msgstr "用于限定状态和可观测性作用域的稳定标识符。"

msgid "The current metric group."
msgstr "当前指标组。"

msgid "The parallelism with which the parallel task runs."
msgstr "并行任务运行时采用的并行度。"

msgid "Runtime info (batching/async) for this task."
msgstr "此任务的运行时信息（批处理/异步）。"

msgid "Index of this parallel subtask (0 .. parallelism-1)."
msgstr "此并行子任务的索引（0 .. parallelism-1）。"

msgid "Task name of the parallel task."
msgstr "并行任务的任务名称。"

msgid "RuntimeContext for streaming execution, adding checkpoint capabilities."
msgstr "用于流处理执行的 RuntimeContext，增加了检查点能力。"

msgid "The strategy used to align and persist checkpoints."
msgstr "用于对齐和持久化检查点的策略。"

msgid "Runtime batching and asynchronous buffering settings."
msgstr "运行时批处理和异步缓冲设置。"

msgid "Function lifecycle"
msgstr "函数生命周期"

msgid "Lifecycle hooks shared by user-defined sources and sinks."
msgstr "用户定义源和 sink 共用的生命周期钩子。"

msgid "Metrics"
msgstr "指标"

msgid ""
"Register a metric once during worker initialization: use "
"``open(runtime_context)`` for a lifecycle source or sink, or request the "
"``runtime_context`` constructor keyword in a callable transform class. "
"Update the returned handle while processing records. Re-registering one "
"name with a different kind, description, boundary set, or label set "
"raises ``ValueError``."
msgstr ""
"在 worker 初始化期间只注册一次指标：生命周期源或 sink 应使用 ``open(runtime_context)``，可调用转换类则应请求 "
"``runtime_context`` 构造函数关键字参数。在处理记录时更新返回的句柄。若以不同的种类、描述、边界集合或标签集合重复注册同一名称，将引发 "
"``ValueError``。"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`metrics` for ``MetricGroup``, metric handles, specifications, "
"and the runtime-owned metric scopes."
msgstr "有关 ``MetricGroup``、指标句柄、规范和运行时拥有的指标作用域，请参阅 :doc:`metrics`。"

msgid "Sink API"
msgstr "Sink API"

msgid ":py:obj:`SinkFunction <ray.klein.SinkFunction>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`SinkFunction <ray.klein.SinkFunction>`"

msgid "Interface for implementing user defined sink functionality."
msgstr "用于实现用户定义 sink 功能的接口。"

msgid ":py:obj:`SinkCommittable <ray.klein.SinkCommittable>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`SinkCommittable <ray.klein.SinkCommittable>`"

msgid "Serializable transaction prepared by a two-phase-commit sink."
msgstr "由两阶段提交 sink 准备的可序列化事务。"

msgid ":py:obj:`StreamSink <ray.klein.StreamSink>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`StreamSink <ray.klein.StreamSink>`"

msgid "A lazy terminal operation registered with its owning pipeline."
msgstr "注册到其所属管道的惰性终端操作。"

msgid ""
":py:obj:`TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction "
"<ray.klein.TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction>`"
msgstr ""
":py:obj:`TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction "
"<ray.klein.TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction>`"

msgid "Sink writer that prepares serializable transactions at checkpoints."
msgstr "在检查点处准备可序列化事务的 sink writer。"

msgid ""
"The checkpoint coordinator persists the committable before invoking "
":meth:`commit`. Implementations must make both ``commit`` and ``abort`` "
"idempotent because coordinator recovery can retry either operation."
msgstr ""
"检查点协调器在调用 :meth:`commit` 前持久化 committable。实现必须使 ``commit`` 和 ``abort`` "
"都具备幂等性，因为协调器恢复时可能重试任一操作。"

msgid "Discard a transaction whose checkpoint cannot complete."
msgstr "丢弃其检查点无法完成的事务。"

msgid "Publish the prepared transaction after checkpoint durability."
msgstr "检查点持久化后发布已准备的事务。"

msgid "Stable idempotency key for this prepared transaction."
msgstr "此已准备事务的稳定幂等键。"

msgid ""
"Records remain private to the writer until :meth:`prepare_commit` returns"
" a committable. The checkpoint coordinator persists that value and "
"performs the second-phase commit only after the global checkpoint is "
"durable."
msgstr ""
"在 :meth:`prepare_commit` 返回 committable 前，记录仅对 writer "
"可见。检查点协调器会持久化该值，并仅在全局检查点持久化后执行第二阶段提交。"

msgid "Custom source API"
msgstr "自定义源 API"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`../connectors/custom` for a complete implementation and :doc"
":`../event-time` for the idle-input and watermark protocol."
msgstr "完整实现请参阅 :doc:`../connectors/custom`，空闲输入和水位线协议请参阅 :doc:`../event-time`。"

msgid "Whether ``collect_many`` is one atomic columnar runtime emission."
msgstr "``collect_many`` 是否构成一次原子的列式运行时发出操作。"

msgid "Emit one record and force its local transport buffers to drain."
msgstr "发出一条记录，并强制排空其本地传输缓冲区。"

msgid "Emit a source batch, falling back to ordered row emission."
msgstr "发出一个源批次；不支持时回退为按序逐行发出。"

msgid "Force buffered source output toward the next task when supported."
msgstr "在支持时强制将缓冲的源输出推向下一任务。"

msgid ""
"Connectors that block-poll an external system (Kafka, etc.) should call "
"this on an empty poll so downstream watermarks are not blocked and the "
"runtime's time-based checkpoint trigger can still fire. A concrete "
"context may implement this as an immediate idle transition."
msgstr ""
"会对外部系统执行阻塞轮询的连接器（Kafka "
"等）应在空轮询时调用此方法，以免阻塞下游水位线，并使运行时基于时间的检查点触发器仍能触发。具体上下文可将其实现为立即进入空闲状态。"

msgid "Lifecycle order"
msgstr "生命周期顺序"

msgid ""
"For each physical source subtask Klein constructs one ``SourceFunction``,"
" calls ``open()``, restores source state when configured, and then calls "
"``run()``. Cancellation calls ``cancel()`` so the run loop can return; "
"``close()`` releases resources once. Completed checkpoints invoke "
"``notify_checkpoint_complete()`` at least once, so external offset "
"commits must be idempotent by checkpoint ID."
msgstr ""
"Klein 会为每个物理源子任务构造一个 ``SourceFunction``，调用 ``open()``，在配置了恢复时恢复源状态，然后调用 "
"``run()``。取消操作调用 ``cancel()``，使运行循环可以返回；``close()`` 只释放资源一次。完成的检查点至少调用一次 "
"``notify_checkpoint_complete()``，因此外部 offset 提交必须按检查点 ID 保证幂等。"

msgid "SQL and table API"
msgstr "SQL 与表 API"

msgid ":py:obj:`sql <ray.klein.sql>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`sql <ray.klein.sql>`"

msgid ""
"Build SQL over named Klein DataStreams, discovering caller variables by "
"default."
msgstr "基于具名 Klein DataStreams 构建 SQL；默认自动发现调用方变量。"

msgid ":py:obj:`SQLQueryError <ray.klein.SQLQueryError>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`SQLQueryError <ray.klein.SQLQueryError>`"

msgid ":py:obj:`SQLSession <ray.klein.SQLSession>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`SQLSession <ray.klein.SQLSession>`"

msgid "A scoped catalog and planner for lazy, Ray-native SQL operations."
msgstr "用于惰性 Ray 原生 SQL 操作的作用域化目录和规划器。"

msgid ":py:obj:`ChangelogRow <ray.klein.ChangelogRow>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`ChangelogRow <ray.klein.ChangelogRow>`"

msgid "A row plus Flink-compatible changelog metadata."
msgstr "一行数据及其 Flink 兼容的 changelog 元数据。"

msgid ":py:obj:`RowKind <ray.klein.RowKind>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`RowKind <ray.klein.RowKind>`"

msgid "Flink-compatible change carried by one dynamic-table row."
msgstr "由一行动态表数据携带的 Flink 兼容变更类型。"

msgid ":py:obj:`CatalogTable <ray.klein.CatalogTable>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`CatalogTable <ray.klein.CatalogTable>`"

msgid "Schema and connector options stored in a :class:`SQLSession` catalog."
msgstr "存储在 :class:`SQLSession` 目录中的 schema 和连接器选项。"

msgid ":py:obj:`TableColumn <ray.klein.TableColumn>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`TableColumn <ray.klein.TableColumn>`"

msgid "One physical column declared by a SQL ``CREATE TABLE`` statement."
msgstr "SQL ``CREATE TABLE`` 语句声明的一个物理列。"

msgid ":py:obj:`TableFactory <ray.klein.TableFactory>`"
msgstr ":py:obj:`TableFactory <ray.klein.TableFactory>`"

msgid "Validate catalog metadata and bind it directly to a source or sink."
msgstr "验证目录元数据，并将其直接绑定到源或 sink。"

msgid "Create or replace a named, non-materialized DataStream view."
msgstr "创建或替换一个具名、非物化的 DataStream 视图。"

msgid "Execute catalog DDL/DML or build a lazy query."
msgstr "执行目录 DDL/DML，或构建惰性查询。"

msgid ""
"``CREATE/DROP TABLE`` update only session metadata. ``INSERT INTO`` "
"builds the query graph and returns its connector sink; normal queries "
"return a :class:`DataStream`."
msgstr ""
"``CREATE/DROP TABLE`` 只更新会话元数据。``INSERT INTO`` 构建查询图并返回其连接器 sink；普通查询返回 "
":class:`DataStream`。"

msgid "Register a session-local table factory."
msgstr "注册会话本地的表工厂。"

msgid "Build a lazy, bounded DataStream from one Ray-native SQL query."
msgstr "从一条 Ray 原生 SQL 查询构建惰性、有界 DataStream。"

msgid "Return changelog changes accepted by this connector sink."
msgstr "返回此连接器 sink 接受的 changelog 变更类型。"

msgid ""
"``row_kind`` is metadata rather than a user column, so normal mapping and"
" connector serialization continue to see only the SQL result columns."
msgstr "``row_kind`` 是元数据而不是用户列，因此常规映射和连接器序列化仍只会看到 SQL 结果列。"

