msgid ""
"Application code normally imports both ``ray`` and ``ray.klein`` and then"
" accesses ``ray.klein``. The following categories are documented "
"application contracts:"
msgstr "应用代码通常同时导入 ``ray`` 和 ``ray.klein``，然后访问 ``ray.klein``。以下类别属于有文档说明的应用契约："

msgid ""
"graph construction and execution: :class:`~ray.klein.DataStream`, "
"``from_items``, ``from_values``, ``source``, ``execute``, ``explain``, "
"and ``sql``;"
msgstr ""
"图构建与执行：:class:`~ray.klein.DataStream`、``from_items``、``from_values``、``source``、``execute``、``explain`` "
"和 ``sql``；"

msgid ""
"jobs and runtime context: :class:`~ray.klein.JobHandle`, "
":class:`~ray.klein.JobStatus`, :class:`~ray.klein.RuntimeContext`, and "
":class:`~ray.klein.RuntimeInfo`;"
msgstr ""
"作业与运行时上下文：:class:`~ray.klein.JobHandle`、:class:`~ray.klein.JobStatus`、:class:`~ray.klein.RuntimeContext`"
" 和 :class:`~ray.klein.RuntimeInfo`；"

msgid ""
"stateful streaming: :class:`~ray.klein.KeyedStream`, "
":class:`~ray.klein.KeyedProcessFunction`, window assigners, and watermark"
" strategies, plus :class:`~ray.klein.api.MissingDataStrategy` for the "
"composite map-reduce preprocessing policy;"
msgstr ""
"有状态流处理：:class:`~ray.klein.KeyedStream`、:class:`~ray.klein.KeyedProcessFunction`、窗口分配器和水位线策略，以及用于组合式"
" map-reduce 预处理策略的 :class:`~ray.klein.api.MissingDataStrategy`；"

msgid ""
"connectors and tables: documented read/write methods, SQL session and "
"table contracts, and custom source/sink interfaces;"
msgstr "连接器与表：已文档化的读写方法、SQL 会话与表契约，以及自定义源/sink 接口；"

msgid ""
"operations: ``configure_logging``, ``list_job_snapshots``, "
"``get_job_snapshot``, ``rescale_operator``, and ``cancel_job``."
msgstr ""
"运维操作：``configure_logging``、``list_job_snapshots``、``get_job_snapshot``、``rescale_operator``"
" 和 ``cancel_job``。"

msgid "Dynamic Ray Data names"
msgstr "动态 Ray Data 名称"

msgid ""
"Public factories discovered from the installed compatible ``ray.data`` "
"module, such as ``ray.klein.read_parquet``, are created lazily and are "
"not enumerated in ``ray.klein.__all__``. Their signatures and "
"documentation come from that Ray version. Use ``dir(ray.klein)`` and "
"``stream.data.available`` when an application must support more than one "
"compatible Ray patch."
msgstr ""
"从已安装且兼容的 ``ray.data`` 模块中发现的公共工厂（例如 ``ray.klein.read_parquet``）会惰性创建，不会列入"
" ``ray.klein.__all__``。其签名和文档来自对应的 Ray 版本。当应用必须支持多个兼容的 Ray 补丁版本时，请使用 "
"``dir(ray.klein)`` 和 ``stream.data.available``。"

msgid "Runtime bridge exports"
msgstr "运行时桥接导出"

msgid ""
"The standalone distribution currently exposes ``get``, ``aget``, "
"``kill``, ``exit_actor``, ``get_actor_by_name``, ``get_actor_status``, "
"``kill_actor_by_name``, ``register_debug_actor``, and ``is_debug_mode`` "
"at the top level because the bundled CLI and runtime share the "
"lightweight Ray/debug adapter. These names originate in "
"``ray.klein._internal`` and are **not** an application compatibility "
"promise. Do not use them to manage arbitrary Ray actors or build user "
"dataflows."
msgstr ""
"独立发行版当前在顶层公开 "
"``get``、``aget``、``kill``、``exit_actor``、``get_actor_by_name``、``get_actor_status``、``kill_actor_by_name``、``register_debug_actor``"
" 和 ``is_debug_mode``，因为随附的 CLI 与运行时共用轻量级 Ray/debug 适配器。这些名称来自 "
"``ray.klein._internal``， **不** 构成应用兼容性承诺。请勿使用它们管理任意 Ray actor 或构建用户数据流。"

msgid ""
"An exported name is not a substitute for the documented API boundary. New"
" application code should use :class:`JobHandle`, the JSON-safe "
"observability API, and Ray's own public APIs instead of these bridge "
"helpers."
msgstr ""
"导出的名称不能替代已文档化的 API 边界。新应用代码应使用 :class:`JobHandle`、JSON 安全的可观测性 API 和 Ray "
"自身的公共 API，而不是这些桥接辅助函数。"

msgid "Import guidance"
msgstr "导入指南"

msgid ""
"Use short imports for ordinary graph code and domain packages for "
"specialized contracts:"
msgstr "普通图代码使用短导入，专用契约使用领域包："

msgid ""
"The public :class:`~ray.klein.StreamSink` type is useful for annotations "
"in advanced selective-execution code; ordinary pipelines do not need to "
"import or pass sink tokens."
msgstr ""
"公共 :class:`~ray.klein.StreamSink` 类型适用于高级选择性执行代码中的类型注解；普通管道无需导入或传递 sink 标记。"

msgid ""
"``ray.klein.runtime`` and ``ray.klein._internal`` are implementation "
"packages. The documented partitioner types are the narrow exception used "
"by ``DataStream.partition_by``."
msgstr ""
"``ray.klein.runtime`` 和 ``ray.klein._internal`` 是实现包。已文档化的分区器类型是一个狭窄例外，供 "
"``DataStream.partition_by`` 使用。"

msgid ""
"See :doc:`../api-stability` for the alpha compatibility categories, "
"deprecation policy, and operational-contract rules."
msgstr "有关 alpha 兼容性类别、弃用政策和运维契约规则，请参阅 :doc:`../api-stability`。"

